thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Rachel P.

author: Rachel P.
title: Rachel P.
text: Glasses were exactly what I expected. Great quality and fast shipping. I was not aware that the duties and taxes were not included in the shipping fees I paid at checkout...an extra 23$ on delivery. Still a $150 less than prices in local stores so I'don't absolutely buy again.
